title: Jezebel Jade (Comico)
description:
Here's a little past-blast: Jezebel Jade, a three-issue mini published in 1988 by Comico, written by William Messner-Loebs, and featuring early artwork from Adam Kubert!

Remember Race Bannon from "Jonny Quest"? Well, turns out that when he was younger (and less of a bottom), he was a government operative who needed the help of a bounty hunter/soldier of fortune (the eponymous Ms. Jade) to close out the case. This here am be that story.

Props to the creative peoples and the scanners! Get it, seed it!
